{"tid":2459164,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"出新書喇: 《羊村清道夫》兒童繪本 - 香港人的抗疫時代","createTime":"2021-03-24T03:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T15:36:41.000Z","uid":52779,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"609919c76294b39ddb798d780c5781c8637e8489","tid":2459164,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:50:20.000Z","msg":"《羊村清道夫》兒童繪本<br />\n<br />\n搶口罩、醫護罷工、停課、599G、限聚令、餐廳禁堂食、封區、疫苗......過往一年相信香港人對呢啲話題都唔陌生。回想返2020年初究竟係咩原因導致香港人要面臨同家屬分離、經濟同生活停頓嘅痛苦？<br />\n<br />\n面對生活入面嘅各種荒謬，我哋更要將真相傳承落去。繪本期望能夠述說疫情嘅真相，同時紀錄低喺危急嘅關頭仍然有香港人願意挺身而出、守衛家園嘅種種時刻。<br />\n<br />\n故事簡介：大灰狼喺羊村嘅圍欄度開咗一個窿，自此每日都有好多隻狼由狼村入去羊村。狼成日都亂拋垃圾，搞到羊村越嚟越污糟，危害到羊咩咩嘅健康。羊小清同其他清道夫唯有透過罷工，期望可以令大灰狼改變心意，閂返個圍欄，佢哋會唔會成功呢？<br />\n<br />\n文：香港言語治療師總工會<br />\n圖：熱奶茶<br />\n<br />\n有實體書嘅店舖list 可以喺我哋fb 專頁 (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheGUHKST/photos/a.119883192803194/305564967568348/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTheGUHKST%2Fphotos%2Fa.119883192803194%2F305564967568348%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2EBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=530cf7bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TheGUHKST/photos/a.119883192803194/305564967568348/?type=3</a>)搵到。<br />\n<br />\n同時多謝 CopyCat Printing Centre 今次依然二話不說肯幫我哋印刷呢本繪本。<br />\n<br />\n店舖地圖可查閱本會網站： <a href=\"http://www.guhkst.org/striketogether\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guhkst.org%2Fstriketogether&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2EBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=47d776a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.guhkst.org/striketogether</a><br />\n<br />\n電子書連結：<a href=\"https://issuu.com/guhkst/docs/____rgb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fissuu.com%2Fguhkst%2Fdocs%2F____rgb&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2EBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=3f0c4534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://issuu.com/guhkst/docs/____rgb</a><br />\n<br />\n「但他知道這篇記事並非紀錄最後的勝利，而是作為見證。 有些人無法成為聖人且容不下疫災，儘管個人心碎痛苦， 仍極盡所能想成為醫者。 這篇記事見證的正是這些人應該做些什麼， 或許以後還得再做些什麼， 以便對抗始終全副武裝的恐懼。」<br />\n 卡繆 《鼠疫》<br />\n<br />\n註：如果有會員希望索取繪本，可以同工會理事聯絡。"},{"pid":"d6f5c7864fe81db11721c630eebec1e5576508df","tid":2459164,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c03b044634d5e30f8780a2d52a85ed7696262cd","tid":2459164,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:50:53.000Z","msg":"Tracy好勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe03c0f5c7b983aae2d614699fd439f4281f423c","tid":2459164,"uid":52779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好快"},{"pid":"ea43f08e793e2af86511eb14993b59302ba3565a","tid":2459164,"uid":52779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c03b044634d5e30f8780a2d52a85ed7696262cd","tid":2459164,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:50:53.000Z","msg":"Tracy好勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哈哈, 好似咩都睇下咁"},{"pid":"0eb118176b87b967653c6cf1c19910de8447d652","tid":2459164,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03